<HEADLINE>
THE FATE OF SIX-YEAR-OLD HAS THE POWER TO MOVE NATIONS    
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Editorial...RESENDING from Mon., April 24)   (This 600-word ``separate-buy'' editorial is from THE INDEPENDENT
newspaper in London.)     
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
