<SLUG> BC-INDIA-BONE-DRY-500&AMP;add-INDEPENDENT-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
DROUGHT REVEALS THE `REAL' INDIA THAT INTERNET BOOM FORGOT    
</HEADLINE>
  
