 c.2000 The Independent, London  
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features)  
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ Jennifer is Jewish, a member of the local, liberal
_ and brave _ little Jewish community in Madison, Wis. She had
helped to arrange my lecture on Iraq and Kosovo.
