at the hole, or you can focus on the glorious circle of yummy
dough. (Rice, Austin-American Statesman) Art includes a 1-column
color photo of a table of doughnuts.
</P>
<P>
   FOOD-FASTCOOK _ Think you don't have time to cook? Master a few
basic techniques_ searing, sauteing and pan sauces_ and you'll have
dinner in a flash. We turned to Pam Anderson, author of How to Cook
Without a Book, and James Peterson, author of The Essentials of
Cooking, for guidance.. (Walker, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) WITH
COLOR PHOTO.
