<P>
   CIR-SIMS-VIRUS (Undated) _ Imagine a computer game in which you
follow all the rules, but your characters still die, because
someone has introduced a virus into the game. Not only that, but
the person who invented the game is the one who is distributing the
virus. Exactly this is happening with Sims, the most recent
creation of Will Wright, the Sim City game designer. By John
Markoff.
