service'' (DoS) attacks that cut off access to some of the Web's
most popular destinations in early February. And that's frightening
to anyone who trades online. A long-term solution to the problem
must be found. Because, until then, nobody is safe...By Greg
Knauss, Worth Magazine &QL;
