civil rights lawsuit filed by Elmer ``Geronimo'' Pratt, bringing an
end to the three-decade legal odyssey of the former Black Panther
whose murder conviction was overturned in 1997 after he had spent
25 years in prison, a third of it in solitary confinement. By Todd
